OL,3,CBoy, 13, killed in crash was 'fun,
OL,4,Cbright, handsome' football lover
OL,6,FThe family of a 13-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied in a crash in Bedfordshire have
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to the "incredibly well-
OL,9,Fliked boy" who loved attending
OL,10,FLiverpool and Luton Town football
OL,11,Fmatches.
OL,13,FNoah Campbell died in the crash
OL,14,Fbetween a car, a bike and a scooter on
OL,15,FGreenfield Road, Flitwick, at 11.50pm
OL,16,Fon Friday.
OL,18,FTwo other teenage boys were taken to
OL,19,Fhospital to be treated for serious
OL,20,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
