PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775412669
OL,3,CBoy, 13, killed in crash was 'fun,
OL,4,Cbright, handsome' football lover
OL,6,FIn a statement issued by Bedfordshire
OL,7,FPolice on Sunday, Noah's family said:
OL,8,F"Noah was a fun, bright, handsome,
OL,9,Fathletic and incredibly well-liked boy.
OL,11,F"Above all else, he cherished spending
OL,12,Ftime with his friends and family; they
OL,13,Fwere the heart of his world.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775412669
OL,3,CBoy, 13, killed in crash was 'fun,
OL,4,Cbright, handsome' football lover
OL,6,F"Noah was a talented and versatile
OL,7,Fsportsman. While football was his
OL,8,Ffavourite sport ` playing for many
OL,9,Flocal teams ` he was a gifted all-
OL,10,Frounder who excelled in rugby, cricket
OL,11,Fand athletics. Outside of organised
OL,12,Fsports, Noah stayed active and
OL,13,Fadventurous; he loved challenging
OL,14,Fhimself at the gym and spending time
OL,15,Fat the bike park.
OL,17,F"Some of his happiest memories were
OL,18,Fmade enjoying attending Liverpool FC
OL,19,Fand Luton Town FC matches alongside
OL,20,Fhis dad.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775412669
OL,3,CBoy, 13, killed in crash was 'fun,
OL,4,Cbright, handsome' football lover
OL,6,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,7,Ftheir kind words and support during
OL,8,Fthis incredibly difficult time."We are
OL,9,Futterly devastated; Noah's death has
OL,10,Fleft a hole in our lives that will
OL,11,Fremain forever."
OL,13,FJamie Fountain, 24, and Ellie Ireland,
OL,14,F23, were charged in connection with
OL,15,Fthe crash.
OL,17,FFountain, of Fir Tree Close, Flitwick,
OL,18,Fwas charged with causing death by
OL,19,Fcareless driving, and causing death by
OL,20,Fcareless driving while over the legal
OL,21,Flimit for alcohol and drugs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`OUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
