PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775412669
OL,3,CBoy, 13, killed in crash was 'fun,
OL,4,Cbright, handsome' football lover
OL,6,FThey have both been remanded in
OL,7,Fcustody to appear before Luton
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Monday.
OL,10,FOf the two other boys who were
OL,11,Finjured, one remains in hospital in a
OL,12,Fserious condition.
OL,14,FThe other was treated for serious
OL,15,Finjuries and has been discharged,
OL,16,Fpolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
