CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775412669
OL,3,CBoy, 13, killed in crash was 'fun,
OL,4,Cbright, handsome' football lover
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Shona Searle, of
OL,7,Fthe Bedfordshire, Cambridgeshire and
OL,8,FHertfordshire serious collision
OL,9,Finvestigation unit, said: "This
OL,10,Fincident has sent shockwaves through
OL,11,Fthe small community of Flitwick and
OL,12,Fthe surrounding area, and we maintain
OL,13,Fa community policing presence around
OL,14,Fthe scene for reassurance.
OL,16,F"While we understand the strong
OL,17,Ffeeling associated with the loss of a
OL,18,Fyoung life, and the serious injury of
OL,19,Fothers, we would ask that people do
OL,20,Fnot speculate on the circumstances of
OL,21,Fthe situation.
OL,26,@qD@[OUxD@AOU
